IMAPStore meain-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port  993
User abinsimon10@gmail.com
PassCmd "keypuller"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

MaildirStore meain-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/meain/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/meain/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel meain
Expunge Both
Master :meain-remote:
Slave :meain-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
ExpireUnread yes
MaxMessages 300
